elements.name: Check that Sign Up Scenario works successfully

steps.name: User visits home page to sign up
User clicks on Sign Up Button
User inputs name, email, password, confirm password and selects a role
User clicks submit sign up button
User receives a sign up success message
Admin visits home page to approve a user
Admin clicks on login button to approve a user
Admin logins with email and password to approve a user
Admin visits Admin Panel to approve a user
Admin clicks on New Accounts tab
Admin approves the first new user
